Encomium Magazine bụ magazin Naijiria nke Encomium Ventures Limited bipụtara
Magazin ahụ amalitela ibipụta kemgbe afọ 1997. Isi ụlọ ọrụ ya dị na Ikeja, Lagos Steeti
Encomium Magazine so n'ime magazin na-ere ahịa n'ụzọ dị nro na Naịjirịa
Mgbasa ozi ya gụnyere asịrị ndị ama ama, ahụike, ụdị na ọdịmma.
